White Zombie - It Came From N.Y.C.. 2016 320ak

   White Zombie was an American heavy metal band that formed in 1985. Based in New York City, White Zombie was originally a noise rock band, and was known for its later heavy metal-oriented sound. The group officially disbanded in 1998. In 2000, White Zombie was included on VH-1's 100 Greatest Artists of Hard Rock,

This is a three-disc anthology of the band White Zombie, released on June 3, 2016. It collects all the material the group officially released between 1985 and 1989, including previously unreleased tracks from 1986. Enjoy and share with others
